about.summary: Scalable Bloom Filter implemented in Python

name: pybloom_live
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set name = "pybloom_live" %}
{% set version = "3.0.0" %}

package:
  name: {{ name|lower }}
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  url: https://pypi.io/packages/source/{{ name[0] }}/{{ name }}/{{ name }}-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: 837550da7c82adb14b901c56c3e131ad269250cd19850a53671e878bd0626c68

build:
  number: 0
  script: "{{ PYTHON }} -m pip install . --no-deps -vv"
  noarch: python

requirements:
  host:
    - python
    - pip
  run:
    - python
    - bitarray >=0.3.4

test:
  imports:
    - pybloom_live

about:
  home: https://github.com/joseph-fox/python-bloomfilter
  license: MIT
  license_family: MIT
  license_file: LICENSE.txt
  summary: 'Scalable Bloom Filter implemented in Python'

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - roll
